<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="91400000t" end="135000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">「約定的夢幻島 S2」</p>
<p begin="159400000t" end="198200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">(回想起來了　回想起來了)</p>
<p begin="199000000t" end="238200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">(在那一眨眼間的絕望感覺)</p>
<p begin="239000000t" end="278200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">(即使醒來了　仍然在夢中)</p>
<p begin="279000000t" end="321800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">(夢見我們剎那光輝的故事)</p>
<p begin="322590000t" end="363000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">(時鐘的秒針)</p>
<p begin="363800000t" end="393000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">(請對我報以微笑吧)</p>
<p begin="393800000t" end="454200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">(滿腦子心心念念的都是你啊)</p>
<p begin="479400000t" end="517800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">(打破冰封三尺的明日吧)</p>
<p begin="518600000t" end="558200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">(盡是些絕對不能失去的事物)</p>
<p begin="559000000t" end="598200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">(我在命運指引的前路上找到了你)</p>
<p begin="599000000t" end="637000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">(如今眼淚已再也沒有意義)</p>
<p begin="637800000t" end="677000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">(在飛快地運轉的世界一角)</p>
<p begin="677800000t" end="718600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">(有如吶喊一樣呼吸著)</p>
<p begin="719400000t" end="757800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">(如能在跨越千千萬萬時光後重逢)</p>
<p begin="758600000t" end="799000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">(就在絕望的前方一步笑吧)</p>
<p begin="1011400000t" end="1029000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">孫居和穆吉卡？</p>
<p begin="1053800000t" end="1084600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">難道邪血少女現在還活著</p>
<p begin="1086600000t" end="1099400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">你說邪血？</p>
<p begin="1100200000t" end="1127000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">原來諾曼你也認識他們嗎</p>
<p begin="1131400000t" end="1156200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">雖然不認識，但也聽過他們的事</p>
<p begin="1159800000t" end="1193400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">有一種鬼從出生開始就沒有吃過人</p>
<p begin="1199000000t" end="1211800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">即使不吃人</p>
<p begin="1213800000t" end="1238600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">也可以維持人的形態及智力</p>
<p begin="1239400000t" end="1251800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">是一種異類</p>
<p begin="1256200000t" end="1285800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">根據記錄，第一次確認他們存在</p>
<p begin="1288200000t" end="1305000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">大約在700年前</p>
<p begin="1305800000t" end="1330200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">這段時間是締結約定之後</p>
<p begin="1331000000t" end="1349800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">確定農場機制之前</p>
<p begin="1355000000t" end="1381400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">他最初出現在飽受饑荒的村落</p>
<p begin="1382200000t" end="1408200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">被視為救世主　　救世主？</p>
<p begin="1414200000t" end="1432600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">他只需要很少量的血</p>
<p begin="1433400000t" end="1458600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">就可以將他的能力傳給其他鬼</p>
<p begin="1463800000t" end="1491400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">簡單來說，鬼只要喝一口他的血</p>
<p begin="1496200000t" end="1527800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">那隻鬼就會變成跟他相同的體質</p>
<p begin="1533400000t" end="1542600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">不僅如此</p>
<p begin="1543400000t" end="1563000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">除了得到跟他相同的體質</p>
<p begin="1563800000t" end="1578600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">還會得到他的能力</p>
<p begin="1583400000t" end="1591400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">那就是…</p>
<p begin="1592200000t" end="1615000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">有辦法增加即使不吃人</p>
<p begin="1615800000t" end="1633000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">也不會退化的鬼的數量嗎</p>
<p begin="1647800000t" end="1667400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">之後，他繼續將他的力量</p>
<p begin="1668200000t" end="1680600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">分給其他鬼</p>
<p begin="1681400000t" end="1701000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">令幾個村落擺脫饑荒</p>
<p begin="1701800000t" end="1717000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">逃過滅村的命運</p>
<p begin="1722600000t" end="1761800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">但是鬼王和鬼貴族知道這件事之後</p>
<p begin="1766600000t" end="1782200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">就捉了他和他的同伴</p>
<p begin="1783000000t" end="1810200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">將擁有那種血統的鬼全都吃掉</p>
<p begin="1826600000t" end="1836600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">記錄上說</p>
<p begin="1837400000t" end="1853800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">邪血少女在那時候被吃掉</p>
<p begin="1854600000t" end="1869800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">應該早就死了</p>
<p begin="1870600000t" end="1883800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">竟然還在生？</p>
<p begin="1888200000t" end="1910600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">他倆一直四處遊歷</p>
<p begin="1911800000t" end="1930200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">原來就是為了逃避追捕</p>
<p begin="1951400000t" end="1979000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">你們說了那麼久，我還是不明白</p>
<p begin="1979800000t" end="2007000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">究竟為何鬼王和鬼貴族</p>
<p begin="2007800000t" end="2031400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">要吃掉穆吉卡和他的同伴？</p>
<p begin="2035400000t" end="2049000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">因為那種血</p>
<p begin="2052200000t" end="2067400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">他們害怕穆吉卡的力量</p>
<p begin="2068200000t" end="2081000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">有甚麼好害怕</p>
<p begin="2081800000t" end="2099800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">我覺得這種力量很好</p>
<p begin="2100600000t" end="2114600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">只要喝了穆吉卡的血</p>
<p begin="2115400000t" end="2136600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">就不用吃人也可以保持人形</p>
<p begin="2137400000t" end="2150200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">因為礙手礙腳</p>
<p begin="2158600000t" end="2176600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">從統治者的角度來看</p>
<p begin="2177400000t" end="2204600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">他們需要控制農場的人肉供應</p>
<p begin="2205400000t" end="2221800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">何時？給誰</p>
<p begin="2222600000t" end="2239400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">通過控制人肉分配</p>
<p begin="2240200000t" end="2257000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">刻意製造階級差距</p>
<p begin="2263400000t" end="2289800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">方便他們隨心所欲地支配世界</p>
<p begin="2293000000t" end="2325400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">所以要趕盡殺絕，然後獨佔市場</p>
<p begin="2327800000t" end="2340600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">我說得對嗎</p>
<p begin="2350200000t" end="2373000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">說不定1000年前的約定也一樣</p>
<p begin="2373800000t" end="2398200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">既然跟人類的戰爭停止了</p>
<p begin="2399000000t" end="2418200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">他們就霸佔著人肉市場</p>
<p begin="2419000000t" end="2433000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">控制食物的源頭</p>
<p begin="2433800000t" end="2457000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">這樣在各方面對他們都有優勢</p>
<p begin="2460600000t" end="2488600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">這樣也行？　　你不用太驚訝</p>
<p begin="2491400000t" end="2516200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">因為自私是人的天性</p>
<p begin="2523000000t" end="2539400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">不是所有人都像艾瑪你這樣</p>
<p begin="2540200000t" end="2559000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">只懂得為其他人著想</p>
<p begin="2580190000t" end="2601000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">我勸你們最好還是提防一下</p>
<p begin="2601800000t" end="2617400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">孫居和穆吉卡</p>
<p begin="2632200000t" end="2648600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">他們擁有那種力量</p>
<p begin="2649400000t" end="2671000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">令已退化的鬼變回人形</p>
<p begin="2675400000t" end="2693400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">這樣會構成我的計劃當中</p>
<p begin="2694200000t" end="2716600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">一個不確定的危險因素</p>
<p begin="2720200000t" end="2742600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">所以必須殺死他們</p>
<p begin="2748600000t" end="2779000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">慢著，不可以這樣對孫居和穆吉卡</p>
<p begin="2779800000t" end="2797800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">他們是朋友，也是恩人</p>
<p begin="2798600000t" end="2823400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">不可以殺他們　　艾瑪</p>
<p begin="2833800000t" end="2854600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">但他們始終是鬼</p>
<p begin="2857000000t" end="2888200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">他們會眼睜睜看著我們殺死鬼嗎</p>
<p begin="2889000000t" end="2902200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">會原諒我們嗎</p>
<p begin="2913000000t" end="2933800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">那麼不滅絕鬼就行了</p>
<p begin="2946200000t" end="2990200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">諾曼，坦白說，我不想殺死鬼</p>
<p begin="3027000000t" end="3048600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">我來就是想跟你談這件事</p>
<p begin="3053000000t" end="3068200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">一定有解決方法的</p>
<p begin="3069000000t" end="3089400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">只要用穆吉卡的血就行了</p>
<p begin="3092600000t" end="3116200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">不，不僅是穆吉卡</p>
<p begin="3117000000t" end="3137000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">還有鬼王和鬼貴族的血</p>
<p begin="3141800000t" end="3172600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">有那些血就不用靠吃人去維持人形</p>
<p begin="3175000000t" end="3199400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">不用再為人肉互相爭鬥</p>
<p begin="3200200000t" end="3231800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">當王族失去優勢，就可以推翻他們</p>
<p begin="3232600000t" end="3245800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">還有管理農場的鬼也…</p>
<p begin="3246600000t" end="3259800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">行不通的，艾瑪</p>
<p begin="3265400000t" end="3275400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">只要鬼想吃</p>
<p begin="3276200000t" end="3297800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">即使沒有必要，也會襲擊人類</p>
<p begin="3301400000t" end="3328600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">其實反過來，人類不也是一樣嗎</p>
<p begin="3330600000t" end="3348200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">假設你最喜歡的食物跟你說</p>
<p begin="3349000000t" end="3361400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">「別吃我」</p>
<p begin="3362200000t" end="3383800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">你會回答「好」，然後不吃它嗎</p>
<p begin="3385800000t" end="3413800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">你會強迫你的兄弟姐妹跟你一樣</p>
<p begin="3414600000t" end="3425800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">忍著不吃嗎</p>
<p begin="3429800000t" end="3453400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">你以為所有鬼都會同情人類</p>
<p begin="3454200000t" end="3475000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">然後強迫自己壓抑食慾嗎</p>
<p begin="3475800000t" end="3496600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">在他們眼中，我們只是食物</p>
<p begin="3497400000t" end="3519400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">那就離開這裡去人類世界吧</p>
<p begin="3520200000t" end="3545000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">米涅瓦先生說過的人類世界</p>
<p begin="3545800000t" end="3567000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">雖然這樣鬼就吃不到人類</p>
<p begin="3567800000t" end="3589000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">但總比要他們滅絕好</p>
<p begin="3605000000t" end="3617000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">在避難所時</p>
<p begin="3617800000t" end="3642200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">我們知道了去人類世界的座標</p>
<p begin="3658600000t" end="3675800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">那個座標已經不能用了</p>
<p begin="3704600000t" end="3729400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">這個情報是蘇米告訴我的</p>
<p begin="3758200000t" end="3779800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">那個座標其實是一扇門</p>
<p begin="3780600000t" end="3807000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">以前那扇門連接兩個世界</p>
<p begin="3807800000t" end="3831000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">但是來往要用的裝置</p>
<p begin="3831800000t" end="3852600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">已經全部被農場破壞了</p>
<p begin="3862600000t" end="3875400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">有另一條路嗎</p>
<p begin="3876200000t" end="3903000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">有另一條路可以通往人類世界嗎</p>
<p begin="3903800000t" end="3939000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">有，還有一扇連接兩個世界的門</p>
<p begin="3945800000t" end="3963800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">就在恩典農場之家</p>
<p begin="4009800000t" end="4025800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">這麼辛苦才能逃跑出來</p>
<p begin="4026600000t" end="4045800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">原來那扇門卻在那裡</p>
<p begin="4046600000t" end="4074200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">不過在那裡不是反而更加好嗎</p>
<p begin="4078200000t" end="4093400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">不行，不可能</p>
<p begin="4098600000t" end="4131800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">那扇門在總部地底深處太危險了</p>
<p begin="4135400000t" end="4147400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">還有一件事</p>
<p begin="4151400000t" end="4168600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">即使通過那扇門</p>
<p begin="4171000000t" end="4184200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">又有誰可以保證</p>
<p begin="4185000000t" end="4205000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">人類世界願意接受我們？</p>
<p begin="4205800000t" end="4221800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">不過米涅瓦先生說…</p>
<p begin="4222600000t" end="4235000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">他已經死了</p>
<p begin="4242600000t" end="4262600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">所有支援者都被殺掉</p>
<p begin="4265400000t" end="4285400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">兇手不是鬼，而是人類</p>
<p begin="4304600000t" end="4317000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">無論是人還是鬼</p>
<p begin="4320200000t" end="4339000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">只要為了自己的利益</p>
<p begin="4339800000t" end="4356600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">多殘忍的事都做得出來</p>
<p begin="4365800000t" end="4389400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">更何況還要通過守門人那關</p>
<p begin="4390200000t" end="4402600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">守門人？</p>
<p begin="4411800000t" end="4430600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">與其選擇一條沒有把握的路</p>
<p begin="4434600000t" end="4463400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">不如在這邊打造人類能生存的地方</p>
<p begin="4470200000t" end="4507400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">我敢斷定如果不將鬼趕盡殺絕</p>
<p begin="4508200000t" end="4527000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">就不會有笑著生活的未來</p>
<p begin="4559400000t" end="4595800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">我承認你的計劃的確是萬無一失</p>
<p begin="4596600000t" end="4623000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">你說得沒錯，不過…</p>
<p begin="4635800000t" end="4667400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">要殺死自己的朋友才能生存的未來</p>
<p begin="4673000000t" end="4692600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">對不起，我一定笑不出來</p>
<p begin="4701800000t" end="4732200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">為了萬無一失，就要用滅絕來解決</p>
<p begin="4733000000t" end="4747000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">這樣真的好嗎</p>
<p begin="4749800000t" end="4773000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">明明有不滅絕也能成功的方法</p>
<p begin="4776200000t" end="4799800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">但你卻堅持連無辜的小孩也殺掉</p>
<p begin="4800600000t" end="4813400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">這樣真的好嗎</p>
<p begin="4818200000t" end="4851000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">無論如何，我都沒辦法認同</p>
<p begin="4860600000t" end="4873400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">雖然沒甚麼把握</p>
<p begin="4874200000t" end="4886600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">但如果有一條路</p>
<p begin="4887400000t" end="4901400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">可以令兩個世界都生存</p>
<p begin="4902200000t" end="4921400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">我一定會放手一搏向前走</p>
<p begin="4924200000t" end="4947000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">如果只想選擇最安全的路</p>
<p begin="4950600000t" end="4973000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">那一開始我們就不應該逃走</p>
<p begin="4982600000t" end="5003400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">結果，我被送出欄了</p>
<p begin="5008200000t" end="5020200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">當時明明是你自己…</p>
<p begin="5021000000t" end="5034600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">想拯救所有食用兒童</p>
<p begin="5035400000t" end="5052600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">就不可以錯過任何一步</p>
<p begin="5065400000t" end="5079800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">這個是唯一的方法</p>
<p begin="5091000000t" end="5115400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">究竟為何你要如此著急</p>
<p begin="5136200000t" end="5159000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">你們走吧，跟其他人在神殿裡等我</p>
<p begin="5159800000t" end="5180590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">等一下，諾曼</p>
<p begin="5206200000t" end="5217400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">諾曼</p>
<p begin="5231790000t" end="5253800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">你又想丟下我們自己離開嗎</p>
<p begin="5265000000t" end="5293800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">不行，我不讓你這麼做</p>
<p begin="5299000000t" end="5324200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">諾曼，無論正確與否</p>
<p begin="5325000000t" end="5340600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">你都必須這麼做嗎</p>
<p begin="5344200000t" end="5369800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">你是發自內心想鬼滅絕</p>
<p begin="5370600000t" end="5389800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">要把他們全部殺死嗎</p>
<p begin="5395400000t" end="5406200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">諾曼</p>
<p begin="5420600000t" end="5434600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">你不痛苦嗎</p>
<p begin="5472200000t" end="5513800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">不會，因為這個是我期待的未來</p>
<p begin="5586200000t" end="5597400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">我明白了</p>
<p begin="5614200000t" end="5629000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">我們做一個交易吧</p>
<p begin="5634200000t" end="5663400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">就由我負責去找孫居和穆吉卡</p>
<p begin="5669800000t" end="5700200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">你不是想找他們嗎？由我幫你去找</p>
<p begin="5715400000t" end="5727000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">交換條件是</p>
<p begin="5727800000t" end="5747800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">放棄你那個滅絕鬼的計劃</p>
<p begin="5759800000t" end="5785800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">給我10天時間，我一定會找到他們</p>
<p begin="5818200000t" end="5825800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">那好吧</p>
<p begin="5839400000t" end="5866600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">但限期是三天　　七天吧</p>
<p begin="5867400000t" end="5875400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">五天</p>
<p begin="5897000000t" end="5914600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">我知道了，一言為定</p>
<p begin="5924600000t" end="5934600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">雷，你怎麼樣</p>
<p begin="5935400000t" end="5950200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">我跟艾瑪一起去找</p>
<p begin="5957400000t" end="5983000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">就這麼決定吧，我等你們五天</p>
<p begin="5985400000t" end="6003800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">如果五天內沒帶他們來</p>
<p begin="6004600000t" end="6019000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">我就按照計劃行動</p>
<p begin="6030200000t" end="6055400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">很感謝你，對我來說已經足夠了</p>
<p begin="6112200000t" end="6128200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">行了，我馬上來</p>
<p begin="6147800000t" end="6158600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">你們兩個</p>
<p begin="6170200000t" end="6183000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">一定要小心</p>
<p begin="6558600000t" end="6575800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">老闆…</p>
<p begin="6588600000t" end="6609800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">這是最後一次實驗過程的記錄</p>
<p begin="6615000000t" end="6628200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">效果跟預期一樣</p>
<p begin="6635800000t" end="6663800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">對了，他們專程來跟你說甚麼</p>
<p begin="6666600000t" end="6687000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">他們求我別滅絕鬼</p>
<p begin="6693800000t" end="6703000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">果然沒猜錯</p>
<p begin="6703800000t" end="6727400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">還有，原來邪血少女還活著</p>
<p begin="6733400000t" end="6744600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">這麼糟糕？</p>
<p begin="6745400000t" end="6768200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">她跟艾瑪他們見過面，還成為朋友</p>
<p begin="6769000000t" end="6793000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">甚麼？跟邪血少女成為朋友？</p>
<p begin="6797400000t" end="6825400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">這件事對我們來說好壞參半</p>
<p begin="6843000000t" end="6874200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">他們居然跟鬼成為朋友？</p>
<p begin="6893800000t" end="6935400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">這也難怪，所以才不想殺死鬼</p>
<p begin="6940200000t" end="6986600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">究竟為甚麼…</p>
<p begin="6987400000t" end="7009400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">不可能發生這種事</p>
<p begin="7013400000t" end="7035000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">那些只是鬼</p>
<p begin="7117400000t" end="7127800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">芭芭拉</p>
<p begin="7132600000t" end="7151000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">我的頭快要裂開了</p>
<p begin="7151800000t" end="7175000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">在Lambda時的後遺症發作，可惡</p>
<p begin="7193800000t" end="7208200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">要快點服用這些藥</p>
<p begin="7225800000t" end="7241800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">最近大家發作的時間</p>
<p begin="7242600000t" end="7261400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">好像變得越來越頻密</p>
<p begin="7264600000t" end="7292200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">希斯洛，還有薩吉，連我也是這樣</p>
<p begin="7299400000t" end="7318600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">看來我們剩餘的時間不多了</p>
<p begin="7335000000t" end="7367400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">你們看到了吧？鬼就是這樣</p>
<p begin="7379400000t" end="7396600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">人類的生命在他們眼中</p>
<p begin="7397400000t" end="7428200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">連死物和畜牲都不如</p>
<p begin="7429000000t" end="7455000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">他們還覺得這麼做是理所當然的</p>
<p begin="7458600000t" end="7484200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">可惡，如果沒有他們…</p>
<p begin="7485000000t" end="7505400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">如果所有鬼都消失的話…</p>
<p begin="7538200000t" end="7552200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">老闆，告訴你吧</p>
<p begin="7562600000t" end="7597000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">剛才我們跟艾瑪、雷談了一會</p>
<p begin="7600600000t" end="7616600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">他們那些天真的傻話</p>
<p begin="7617400000t" end="7632200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">真的令我想作嘔</p>
<p begin="7633000000t" end="7657000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">雖然我也知道他們一定是好人</p>
<p begin="7663400000t" end="7683000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">始終是老闆的家人</p>
<p begin="7693000000t" end="7715000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">不過即使如此</p>
<p begin="7718600000t" end="7738200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">你也會站在我們這邊，對吧</p>
<p begin="7740600000t" end="7754200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">你還是我們的老闆</p>
<p begin="7755000000t" end="7771400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">你應該不會動搖吧</p>
<p begin="7963800000t" end="7978600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">為何你要答應</p>
<p begin="7982200000t" end="8003400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">這是真的嗎？如果他們找到</p>
<p begin="8004200000t" end="8020600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">你真的會放棄滅絕計劃嗎</p>
<p begin="8028600000t" end="8040200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">當然不會</p>
<p begin="8060600000t" end="8094200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">一切照舊，還會殺掉邪血</p>
<p begin="8095000000t" end="8119000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">我絕對不會改變我的計劃</p>
<p begin="8238600000t" end="8281000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">既然走到這一步，我當然不會回頭</p>
<p begin="8339800000t" end="8353000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">肚子很餓</p>
<p begin="8359800000t" end="8385400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">要等艾瑪和雷回來才可以吃飯</p>
<p begin="8386200000t" end="8401400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">我也知道</p>
<p begin="8402200000t" end="8427400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">話說回來，還記得孫居說過</p>
<p begin="8428200000t" end="8450200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">這個時期的候鳥特別美味嗎</p>
<p begin="8451000000t" end="8477800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">對，穆吉卡還煮得特別美味</p>
<p begin="8509400000t" end="8527400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">不知道現在他們過得如何</p>
<p begin="8528200000t" end="8541400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">應該不錯吧</p>
<p begin="8575000000t" end="8591000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">甚麼…</p>
<p begin="8595800000t" end="8618200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">你們要去找孫居和穆吉卡？</p>
<p begin="8621000000t" end="8640200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">還要在五天之內找到？</p>
<p begin="8641000000t" end="8658200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">我太衝動了嗎</p>
<p begin="8659000000t" end="8683400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">你也知道嗎？還有你在說甚麼</p>
<p begin="8684200000t" end="8698200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">甚麼不用滅絕鬼</p>
<p begin="8699000000t" end="8719800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">那麼諾曼說的計劃怎麼辦</p>
<p begin="8722600000t" end="8739400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">究竟為甚麼？艾瑪</p>
<p begin="8740200000t" end="8759000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">難道你不怕鬼嗎</p>
<p begin="8766600000t" end="8798200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">不是，我當然害怕，而且很討厭鬼</p>
<p begin="8799000000t" end="8825400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">但我一直在想</p>
<p begin="8831800000t" end="8856200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">在村子裡過著平凡生活的鬼</p>
<p begin="8858200000t" end="8877000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">還有小孩、嬰兒</p>
<p begin="8877800000t" end="8898200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">還有那位瞎了的鬼伯伯</p>
<p begin="8901800000t" end="8932200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">你們真的認為要將他們全部殺掉嗎</p>
<p begin="8943800000t" end="8960200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">雖然我不想被鬼吃掉</p>
<p begin="8966600000t" end="8991800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">但我明白鬼是為了生存才吃人</p>
<p begin="8993800000t" end="9027800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">這樣鬼跟我們的情況不就是一樣嗎</p>
<p begin="9062200000t" end="9091000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">斷絕鬼的糧食，令他們退化</p>
<p begin="9091800000t" end="9123800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">讓同伴和家人之間自相殘殺</p>
<p begin="9124600000t" end="9140200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">然後滅絕這種事</p>
<p begin="9141000000t" end="9168600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">會為他們帶來多少恐怖及憎恨</p>
<p begin="9235800000t" end="9246600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">有時肚子太餓</p>
<p begin="9247400000t" end="9263000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">就會不懂得分辨對與錯</p>
<p begin="9263800000t" end="9275000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">接著就會…</p>
<p begin="9360200000t" end="9384200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">如果可以選擇，我不想殺死鬼</p>
<p begin="9385000000t" end="9403800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">同樣地我不想其他人殺他們</p>
<p begin="9404600000t" end="9416200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">而且最重要的是</p>
<p begin="9417000000t" end="9439000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">可能連孫居和穆吉卡也會被殺掉</p>
<p begin="9450200000t" end="9466600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">所以要阻止滅絕計劃</p>
<p begin="9467400000t" end="9492600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">雖然我不知道這麼做到底是否正確</p>
<p begin="9497400000t" end="9536600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">但我寧願選擇一個不會後悔的未來</p>
<p begin="9542200000t" end="9554600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">未來？</p>
<p begin="9605000000t" end="9627800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">為甚麼　　吉爾妲</p>
<p begin="9628600000t" end="9656600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">就是說要救的不僅是穆吉卡和孫居</p>
<p begin="9657400000t" end="9681000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">連襲擊我們的鬼也要救嗎</p>
<p begin="9685400000t" end="9721000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">你忘記了我們昨天差點被鬼殺死嗎</p>
<p begin="9722200000t" end="9744600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">她這裡一向都有問題</p>
<p begin="9757000000t" end="9782200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">不過這樣才像艾瑪</p>
<p begin="9784600000t" end="9809400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">放心，我會幫助你　　唐</p>
<p begin="9810200000t" end="9825400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">既然艾瑪已經將她的理由</p>
<p begin="9826200000t" end="9838600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">解釋得如此清楚</p>
<p begin="9839400000t" end="9859800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">做不後悔的選擇</p>
<p begin="9860600000t" end="9891000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">不就是我們一直以來所做的事嗎</p>
<p begin="9891800000t" end="9918600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">而且即使阻止她，她也不會聽的</p>
<p begin="9919400000t" end="9940600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">不過，枉我還以為</p>
<p begin="9941400000t" end="9971800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">艾瑪以後都不用再做那些拚命的事</p>
<p begin="9975000000t" end="9994200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">為何又要主動出頭</p>
<p begin="9995000000t" end="10007000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">吉爾妲</p>
<p begin="10030200000t" end="10063400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">對不起，我經常讓你擔心我</p>
<p begin="10069800000t" end="10096200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">但這條路是我自己覺得</p>
<p begin="10097000000t" end="10113000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">最可以接受的路</p>
<p begin="10116600000t" end="10168600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">而且我不想諾曼再為我們犧牲自己</p>
<p begin="10176600000t" end="10185400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">諾曼？</p>
<p begin="10186200000t" end="10224600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">對，他打算再做相同的事</p>
<p begin="10233800000t" end="10262200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">他現在又想為了我們承擔一切</p>
<p begin="10263000000t" end="10277400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">打算做個了結</p>
<p begin="10278190000t" end="10309800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">我和艾瑪還是無法接受要靠他出欄</p>
<p begin="10310600000t" end="10323000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">我們才能逃走</p>
<p begin="10325790000t" end="10347000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">那次根本就不算是成功</p>
<p begin="10350990000t" end="10366190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">雖然大家努力了那麼久</p>
<p begin="10367000000t" end="10382200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">事情還沒完結</p>
<p begin="10386600000t" end="10398190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">但對我們來說</p>
<p begin="10399000000t" end="10418190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">從諾曼離開的那一刻起</p>
<p begin="10421400000t" end="10449000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">那次逃走就不算是真正的成功</p>
<p begin="10455790000t" end="10477800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">我不想他再經歷相同的事</p>
<p begin="10478590000t" end="10493000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">我要保護他</p>
<p begin="10493800000t" end="10512600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">這次我要證明給諾曼看</p>
<p begin="10513400000t" end="10537000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">很多事情沒試過就不知道是否可行</p>
<p begin="10545400000t" end="10580600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">怎麼搞的？諾曼還是一點也沒變</p>
<p begin="10581400000t" end="10601400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">對我們有點信心也不行嗎</p>
<p begin="10602200000t" end="10613800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">對…</p>
<p begin="10614600000t" end="10634200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336">即使當時諾曼沒有被送出欄</p>
<p begin="10635000000t" end="10653400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">我們也可以成功逃走</p>
<p begin="10654200000t" end="10670200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338">一定要證明給他看</p>
<p begin="10684200000t" end="10719000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339">所以吉爾妲，你願意幫我</p>
<p begin="10723800000t" end="10744200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340">跟我一起去找他們嗎</p>
<p begin="10768200000t" end="10791800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341">單憑我和艾瑪的力量還不足夠</p>
<p begin="10795000000t" end="10815000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342">唐，你也一起去吧</p>
<p begin="10824600000t" end="10844200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343">當然，還用說嗎</p>
<p begin="10915000000t" end="10931800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344">你不想去嗎</p>
<p begin="10947800000t" end="10959000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345">不是</p>
<p begin="10973800000t" end="10988200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346">我跟你們一起去</p>
<p begin="11016600000t" end="11042200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347">但事先說明，既然我跟你一起去</p>
<p begin="11043000000t" end="11063400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348">就不會讓你做危險的事</p>
<p begin="11068200000t" end="11091000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349">好，我知道了</p>
<p begin="11109800000t" end="11131400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350">謝謝你，吉爾妲</p>
<p begin="11145400000t" end="11157000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351">不過</p>
<p begin="11157800000t" end="11187400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352">孫居和穆吉卡現時在哪裡</p>
<p begin="11188200000t" end="11210600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353">應該已經離開那個森林了</p>
<p begin="11225400000t" end="11250200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354">正值這個時期，他們說不定…</p>
<p begin="11257000000t" end="11269000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355">對…</p>
<p begin="11273400000t" end="11289400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356">是候鳥…</p>
<p begin="11292200000t" end="11318600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357">對了，這裡是候鳥的必經之地</p>
<p begin="11319400000t" end="11346200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358">為了打獵候鳥，他們可能會來這裡</p>
<p begin="11347000000t" end="11381000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359">那好吧，一定要把他們找出來</p>
<p begin="11383400000t" end="11403800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360">交給你們了　　小心點</p>
<p begin="11404600000t" end="11423000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361">我們會好好守著這裡</p>
<p begin="11423800000t" end="11451400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362">還會用無線電收聽孤兒院的情況</p>
<p begin="11452200000t" end="11487400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363">你們…好吧，交給你們吧</p>
<p begin="11497000000t" end="11521800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364">等我，諾曼</p>
<p begin="11784200000t" end="11803400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365">艾瑪、雷</p>
<p begin="11841400000t" end="11853400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366">對不起</p>
<p begin="11887400000t" end="11899000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367">艾瑪</p>
<p begin="11912200000t" end="11923400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368">謝謝你</p>
<p begin="11946600000t" end="11961000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369">欺騙了你，對不起</p>
<p begin="12037400000t" end="12063800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370">沒事的，你千萬別放棄</p>
<p begin="12549800000t" end="12560200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371">這邊</p>
<p begin="12576200000t" end="12601000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372">你進去這個房間裡面等一會吧</p>
<p begin="12700200000t" end="12711400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373">晚安</p>
<p begin="12717000000t" end="12742600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374">很高興認識你，諾曼</p>
<p begin="12831400000t" end="12857800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375">(當你許下願望)</p>
<p begin="12858600000t" end="12885000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376">(月亮就灑下了影子)</p>
<p begin="12885800000t" end="12941800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377">(像魔法一般的夜晚必定融化無蹤)</p>
<p begin="13049800000t" end="13076200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378">(以澄澈響亮的聲音)</p>
<p begin="13077000000t" end="13103400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379">(風宣布了夜色來臨)</p>
<p begin="13104200000t" end="13130600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380">(藍色世界的一切)</p>
<p begin="13131400000t" end="13158200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381">(都在童話裡沉睡)</p>
<p begin="13159000000t" end="13185000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382">(你在半夢半醒之間)</p>
<p begin="13185800000t" end="13211800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383">(張開了閉著的眼瞼)</p>
<p begin="13212600000t" end="13237000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384">(比我心裡所想的)</p>
<p begin="13237800000t" end="13273400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385">(還要更加朦朧)</p>
<p begin="13289800000t" end="13338200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386">(如果這聲音能傳達)</p>
<p begin="13339000000t" end="13365000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387">(即使得不到回應　也想在你身旁)</p>
<p begin="13365800000t" end="13397400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388">(不想讓這個故事畫下句點)</p>
<p begin="13398200000t" end="13447000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389">(跨越長夜而去吧)</p>
<p begin="13447800000t" end="13473000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle390">(跟你在一起　就再也不需要言語)</p>
<p begin="13473800000t" end="13520200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle391">(如今只想確認彼此的溫度)</p>
<p begin="13521000000t" end="13556200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle392">(讓我沉入不會醒的美夢吧)</p>
<p begin="13557000000t" end="13603000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle393">(我們緊握著那雙手)</p>
<p begin="13603800000t" end="13632600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle394">(靜靜地祈願著)</p>
</div>
